history.content:
Founded in 2015, Qualia transforms real estate closings from an in-person, paper-based process into a fully digital experience. Through a cloud-based platform, it empowers teams to deliver a best-in-class closing experience.
 
Qualia will be hosting an infosession TOMORROW, Wednesday, February 10th at 4pm. Come to hear more about the company and participate in a Q&A! Representatives will also be discussing full-time technical roles for new grads.
 
More info on our Facebook event page: https://fb.me/e/NLlZva90
